#: ../../releases/v3.0.1.rst:7
msgid ""
"The interface of `tornado.auth.FacebookGraphMixin` is now consistent with"
" its documentation and the rest of the module.  The "
"``get_authenticated_user`` and ``facebook_request`` methods return a "
"``Future`` and the ``callback`` argument is optional."
msgstr ""

#: ../../releases/v3.0.1.rst:11
msgid ""
"The `tornado.testing.gen_test` decorator will no longer be recognized as "
"a (broken) test by ``nose``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../releases/v3.0.1.rst:13
msgid ""
"Work around a bug in Ubuntu 13.04 betas involving an incomplete backport "
"of the `ssl.match_hostname` function."
msgstr ""

#: ../../releases/v3.0.1.rst:15
msgid ""
"`tornado.websocket.websocket_connect` now fails cleanly when it attempts "
"to connect to a non-websocket url."
msgstr ""

#: ../../releases/v3.0.1.rst:17
msgid ""
"`tornado.testing.LogTrapTestCase` once again works with byte strings on "
"Python 2."
msgstr ""

#: ../../releases/v3.0.1.rst:19
msgid ""
"The ``request`` attribute of `tornado.httpclient.HTTPResponse` is now "
"always an `~tornado.httpclient.HTTPRequest`, never a ``_RequestProxy``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../releases/v3.0.1.rst:21
msgid ""
"Exceptions raised by the `tornado.gen` module now have better messages "
"when tuples are used as callback keys."
msgstr ""

